{"tid":975983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網路短片「先審後播」 中國網友崩潰：為啥不讓言論自由？","createTime":"2019-01-10T05:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T05:40:04.000Z","uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"adc4d9d095c21a844743efd2d750d90a47389e69","tid":975983,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpwjjCaH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpwjjCaH.jpg&h=0a4a1d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中國今（9日）天公布「網絡短視頻平台管理規範」，要求中國影音平台在未來建立「先審後播」制度，並要求網路短片應該圍繞弘揚社會主義核心價值觀，以提供正向、優質的影片內容。（美聯社）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國今（9日）天公布「網絡短視頻平台管理規範」，要求中國影音平台在未來建立「先審後播」制度，並要求網路短片應該圍繞弘揚社會主義核心價值觀，以提供正向、優質的影片內容。政令公布後，立刻在微博上掀起議論，有中國網友憤怒高喊「為啥不讓言論自由」？<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞報導，由於近年來抖音、快手等平台的手機短片及用戶數量大增，中國昨日公布了「網絡短視頻平台管理規範」，不但要求網路影音平台影片內容要不違反「分裂國家」、「攻擊國家法律與制度內容」、「宣揚迷信」、「宣揚消極頹廢的人生觀」等21項規定，更要求影片內容應「弘揚社會主義」，甚至連彈幕（觀眾的即時留言）都要嚴加管制，希望能以此提供正面的影片內容。<br />\n<br />\n相關政令公布後也立刻引起中國網友嘩然，網友紛紛在微博上崩潰表示「10秒的短片也得審？」、「說出去的話你們要審核一遍，我們還有必要說嗎？」、「我們就是豬，你們餵我們甚麼，我們不敢不吃」、「有毛病吧，言論自由何在？」、「浪費社會資源搞這些東西」、「封殺抖音」、「到底為啥不讓言論自由？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2667100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2667100&d=NJS9iWJNrGuYhPFqm1V0FJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c16fadf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2667100&h=3100af47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2667100</a>"},{"pid":"6d946da485103529d6ccbc8e6addeeafe8636a6c","tid":975983,"uid":34410,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"中國人講言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  今年最大笑話黎?"},{"pid":"62681f2e1b7b9b0bd777f9dea1f2f12308f79623","tid":975983,"uid":76216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"佢地曾幾何時覺得有自由過？"},{"pid":"c4bf6a31c24982a26c9c509a495d7bdfc7beca25","tid":975983,"uid":15830,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"第一日知支那無言論自由？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2766144c6ad83d569069671558fa29333b2ba23","tid":975983,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D9pXHwQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FD9pXHwQ.png&h=5977df3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dYGXoOC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdYGXoOC.png&h=fca7ee06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nJ8pe4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnJ8pe4p.png&h=234a17c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WHUqIEO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWHUqIEO.png&h=dfb1de41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/whjgKuU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwhjgKuU.png&h=46ea779d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7bbu5mB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7bbu5mB.png&h=447c80ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9Gylr9g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9Gylr9g.png&h=6bc9fe85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/b1AthFO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fb1AthFO.png&h=2afeac1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rgcBoVd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com